    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <Text>INT. PAULA'S APT NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Little standing away from Paula, face open and curious as we see what he sees: an average, working class black man -- longshoreman type -- sitting at the small dining table just off the kitchen.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
