    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Typical high school cafeteria landscape, cool kids wedged into tables to themselves, jocks wedged into tables by themselves, band kids not eating at all, just air-playing their sets, particularly the drum-line, forever table- tapping.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
