      <Text>INT. HIGH SCHOOL, CAFETERIA DAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Chiron moves through this mayhem, scanning the room for something, anything inviting. As he passes a group of girls, he spots Kevin sitting by himself.</Text>
