    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Chiron’s eyes light up but he checks himself, doesn’t want to appear too obvious. He begins to take the longest route to get to where Kevin is but, before he can get halfway through his journey... Terrell sits in front of Kevin.</Text>
