    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>We’ve not seen the full of this school yet. It goes like this: upon entering the guard gate and steps aforementioned, one enters what’s best described as a tunnel, passing the admin suites and principals offices and ultimately spilling into this atrium with three stories of classrooms above and around on four sides, the doors all facing in on this courtyard.</Text>
