    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Scene Heading">
      <Text>INT. HIGH SCHOOL, COURTYARD DAY LATER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The boys have surrounded Chiron and Kevin. Kevin steps inside the circle, meets Chiron’s eyes for the briefest moment...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>...and wallops Chiron, the force of it rocking Chiron back, sends him down to one knee clutching his jaw.</Text>
