    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>TERRELL</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>He want to get up? Knock his faggot ass back down.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Chiron taking a few steps closer to Kevin now, comes right up to him, meets his gaze, chin raised.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
